<h2>Guidelines</h2>

<div class="box">
  <ul>
    <li>Obey all traffic laws.</li>
    <li>Don't cross the yellow line.</li>
    <li>Wear your helmet.</li>
    <li>Ride fast and have fun.</li>
  </ul>

  <p>Don't attack on the neutral rollout.</p>

  <p>If you are feeling in over your head or can't rotate through all the way,
  slowly drift to the back and just sit on.</p>

  <p>Always ride in a double or single pace line.</p>  
</div>
